FILE NAMES

	Post186enh_bin.lha
		full distribution (except source code), contains all
		fonts from the GNU GhostScript distribution (which are
		themselves PD or covered by GNU Copyleft)
	Post186enh_min.lha
		All binaries, but only one font -- Funkyfont, which came
		with Post 1.7.  This file is all you'll need if you already
		have a set of Adobe type 1 or type 3 fonts.
	Post186enh_src.lha
		Source code for all the binaries.  Every effort has been made
		to make these files compliant with SAS/C 6.x format.

